            "content": "<ul><li><strong>State:<\/strong> {{ product.metafields.vinyl.state.value }}<\/li><li><strong>Sleeve Grading:<\/strong> {{ product.metafields.garimpo.estado_capa.value }}<\/li><li><strong>Record Grading: <\/strong>{{ product.metafields.garimpo.estado_midia.value }}<\/li><\/ul><h6>What does the Sleeve and Record grading mean? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.goldminemag.com\/collector-resources\/collecting-101-grading-your-records\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.goldminemag.com\/collector-resources\/collecting-101-grading-your-records\">Click here<\/a>.<\/h6>",
